          <text><![CDATA[<p><strong>Prevent Impaired Driving Child Endangerment Act</strong></p> <p>This bill directs the Department of Transportation to withhold from states allocations of transportation funding unless such states enact and enforce certain laws with respect to an individual who is charged with driving a motor vehicle, with a child passenger, while intoxicated or impaired by alcohol, drugs, or a combination of substances. </p>]]></text>
